---
import { Check, X } from 'lucide-astro';
---
<section id="inversion" class="py-24 bg-z-light relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal-up">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-z-dark sm:text-4xl text-balance">El fin de las cuotas mensuales</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-z-blue-dark max-w-2xl mx-auto">Invierte una vez, úsalo para siempre. Diseñado para negocios que quieren maximizar su rentabilidad sin depender de alquileres de software.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto group/pricing">
            
            <!-- Competitors Card (Loss Aversion & Contrast Effect) -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full reveal-up delay-100 transition-all duration-500 group-hover/pricing:opacity-50 group-hover/pricing:blur-xs group-hover/pricing:grayscale hover:opacity-100! hover:blur-none! hover:grayscale! hover:scale-105 hover:z-20 hover:shadow-xl">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-slate-300"></div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-500 mb-2">Sistemas Web (Comunes)</h3>
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">$100+ <span class="text-base font-medium text-slate-500">/ mes</span></div>
                <div class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-red-50 text-red-600 text-xs font-bold mb-6 border border-red-100">
                    <X class="w-3 h-3 mr-1" /> Gasto anual: $1,200+ irrecuperables
                </div>
                
                <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 grow">
                    <li class="flex items-start text-slate-600">
                        <X class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mr-3 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                        <span>Pago eterno de cuotas mensuales.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start text-slate-600">
                        <X class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mr-3 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                        <span>Si se corta Internet, <strong class="text-slate-800">tu negocio se detiene por completo</strong>.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start text-slate-600">
                        <X class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mr-3 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                        <span>Servidores lentos en horarios pico.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start text-slate-600">
                        <X class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mr-3 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                        <span>Tus datos residen en la nube de un tercero.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Zenith Card (Anchor & Value) -->
            <div class="bg-z-dark rounded-2xl p-8 border border-z-gold/30 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full z-10 reveal-up delay-200 transition-all duration-500 group-hover/pricing:opacity-50 group-hover/pricing:blur-xs group-hover/pricing:grayscale hover:opacity-100! hover:blur-none! hover:grayscale! hover:scale-105 hover:z-20 hover:shadow-z-blue/20">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -translate-y-12 translate-x-1/3 w-64 h-64 bg-z-gold/20 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
                <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-z-blue text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider w-max mb-4">
                    Licencia Vitalicia
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Zenith POS</h3>
                <div class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">Pago Único</div>
                <p class="text-z-gold mb-6 font-medium">El software es 100% tuyo, para siempre.</p>
                
                <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10 grow">
                    <li class="flex items-start text-z-light/90">
                        <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-z-gold mr-3 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                        <span>Sin suscripciones, licenciamiento vitalicio.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start text-z-light/90">
                        <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-z-gold mr-3 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                        <span class="relative group/tooltip cursor-help decoration-z-gold/50 underline underline-offset-4 decoration-dotted">
                            Base de datos <strong class="text-white">SQLite local (offline-first)</strong>
                            <span class="absolute bottom-full left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 mb-2 w-64 p-3 bg-white text-z-dark text-xs rounded-lg shadow-xl opacity-0 translate-y-2 pointer-events-none group-hover/tooltip:opacity-100 group-hover/tooltip:translate-y-0 transition-all z-50 border border-z-blue/10">
                                Tu información no viaja por internet. Se guarda blindada en tu PC. Si se cae el WiFi, sigues vendiendo sin interrupciones.
                                <span class="absolute top-full left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 border-8 border-transparent border-t-white"></span>
                            </span>
                        </span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start text-z-light/90">
                        <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-z-gold mr-3 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                        <span>Adaptación visual gratuita (Logo y colores).</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start text-z-light/90">
                        <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-z-gold mr-3 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                        <span>Soporte técnico remoto básico sin cargo.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start text-z-light/90">
                        <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-z-gold mr-3 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                        <span>Compatibilidad absoluta (Win XP a Win 11).</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <a href="#contacto" class="block w-full text-center px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-white bg-linear-to-r from-z-blue to-z-blue-dark hover:from-z-blue-dark hover:to-z-dark border border-z-blue/50 shadow-lg shadow-z-blue/20 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    Consultar Valor del Pago Único
                </a>
                
                <div class="mt-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-z-light/40 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3 h-3 text-z-gold" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
                    Garantía de soporte e instalación incluída
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
